### Health check
GET http://localhost:8787/health

### Database health check
GET http://localhost:8787/health/db

### ── Auth ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login as Alice
POST http://localhost:8787/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "alice123"
}

### Login as Bob
POST http://localhost:8787/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "bob",
  "password": "wrong"
}

### Invalid credentials
POST http://localhost:8787/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "alice123"
}

### ── Items (Alice) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all items (active + history)
GET http://localhost:8787/items
X-User-Id: user_alice

### Get only active items (current shopping list)
GET http://localhost:8787/items?status=active
X-User-Id: user_alice

### Get only history items (known items)
GET http://localhost:8787/items?status=history
X-User-Id: user_alice

### Add new item to list
POST http://localhost:8787/items
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user_alice

{
  "name": "Milk",
  "notes": "2 litres, full fat"
}

### Add item without notes
POST http://localhost:8787/items
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user_alice

{
  "name": "Milk"
}

### Re-add a known item (history → active)
POST http://localhost:8787/items
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user_alice

{
  "name": "Milk",
  "notes": "2 litre this time"
}

### Autocomplete search
GET http://localhost:8787/items/autocomplete?q=mi
X-User-Id: user_alice

### Update notes on an item
PATCH http://localhost:8787/items/REPLACE_WITH_ID/notes
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user_alice

{
  "notes": "3 bananas"
}

### Mark item as bought (active → history + purchase event)
POST http://localhost:8787/items/REPLACE_WITH_ID/bought
X-User-Id: user_alice

### Remove from list (active → history, no purchase event)
POST http://localhost:8787/items/REPLACE_WITH_ID/remove
X-User-Id: user_alice

### Snooze item (suppress from suggestions for 1 day)
POST http://localhost:8787/items/REPLACE_WITH_ID/snooze
X-User-Id: user_alice

### Get derived cadence for item
GET http://localhost:8787/items/REPLACE_WITH_ID/cadence
X-User-Id: user_alice

### ── Suggestions & Summary ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get suggestions (cadence-driven, history items only)
GET http://localhost:8787/suggestions
X-User-Id: user_alice

### Get daily summary
GET http://localhost:8787/summary/daily
X-User-Id: user_alice

### ── Notifications ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get notification history
GET http://localhost:8787/notifications/history

### ── Bob (separate user data) ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Bob's shopping list
GET http://localhost:8787/items?status=active
X-User-Id: user_bob

### Add item for Bob
POST http://localhost:8787/items
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user_bob

{
  "name": "Bread",
  "notes": "sourdough"
}
